# Project briefing (contains operational details)
project-briefing.md

# Local survey/recon notes (not for commit)
ccp-desktop-survey-*.md
ConditioningControlPanel/docs/surveys/

# Internal planning/docs (not for PRs)
ConditioningControlPanel/docs/internal/

# Stray PowerShell PNG outputs that landed at the wrong path
# (System.Drawing.Drawing2D.* etc., from failed Add-Type scratch scripts).
# Root-anchored so legit deeper-tree files matching the pattern aren't excluded.
/ConditioningControlPanel/System.Drawing.*

# Claude Code local config
.claude/
ConditioningControlPanel/.claude/
.github/agents/wpf-ui-specialist.agent.md
AGENTS.md

